American Finance Trust, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 1:50 AM ET
Equity Real Estate Investment Trusts (REITs)

Company Overview of American Finance Trust, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
American Finance Trust, Inc. is a real estate investment trust launched and managed by American Financial Advisors, LLC. It invests in real estate markets of United States. The fund invests in diversified portfolio of commercial properties comprised primarily of freestanding single-tenant properties that are net leased to investment grade and other creditworthy tenants. It was formerly known as American Realty Capital Trust V, Inc. American Finance Trust, Inc. was formed on January 22, 2013 and is based in the United States.


80 State StreetAlbany, NY 12207-2543United StatesFounded in 2013



www.americanfinancetrust.com







